{\displaystyle \Gamma (4.5)=3.5!=\Pi (3.5)={1 \over 2}\cdot {3 \over 2}\cdot {5 \over 2}\cdot {7 \over 2}{\sqrt {\pi }}={8! \over 4^{4}4!}{\sqrt {\pi }}={7! \over 2^{7}3!}{\sqrt {\pi }}={105 \over 16}{\sqrt {\pi }}\approx 11.63.}



