{\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}n!&=\prod _{k=1}^{n}k\\&=1\cdot 2\cdot 3\cdots (n-2)\cdot (n-1)\cdot n\\&=n(n-1)(n-2)\cdots (2)(1)\\\end{aligned}}}



