1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + ⋯
1 + 2 + 4 + 8 + ⋯
1 − 1 + 1 − 1 + ⋯ (Grandi's series)
Infinite arithmetic series
1 − 2 + 3 − 4 + ⋯
1 − 2 + 4 − 8 + ⋯
1 + 1/2 + 1/3 + 1/4 + ⋯ (harmonic series)
1 − 1 + 2 − 6 + 24 − 120 + ⋯ (alternating factorials)
1/2 + 1/3 + 1/5 + 1/7 + 1/11 + ⋯ (inverses of primes)








